            "row_content": "<p>We offer a few easy ways to pay depending on your account type:</p><ul><li><strong>Standard Orders:</strong> We securely accept all major debit and credit cards at checkout.</li><li><strong>Corporate & Credit Customers:</strong> Approved account holders can pay via direct debit on the 20th of the month following the invoice.</li></ul>",
