            "row_content": "<p>If you happen to receive goods that are damaged, expired, or short-dated, please let us know within 24 to 48 hours of delivery so we can help make it right! We will always try to collect the items using our own vans on a future route. However, if a van pickup isn't possible, return shipping costs will need to be covered by the customer</p>",
