            "row_heading_tag": "h3",
            "row_content": "<p>We understand that plans change! If you need to modify or cancel your order, please reach out to our team as soon as possible at admin@worthyproducts.nz or call us on 09 580 4110. We work hard to process and ship orders quickly, so if your order has already been dispatched from our warehouse, we unfortunately won't be able to make any changes or cancel it.<br/><br/></p>",
